scene.message:
Nanjo: {ctl0f:1},{nl}
it seems you've been{nl}
mistaken for someone else.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Someone's been sneaking{nl}
in and out of an empty{nl}
classroom on the 2nd floor...{nl}
You know who that is?{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: I was explaining what{nl}
happened to Ms. Saeko.{waitkey}{clearbox}Brown slipped out early,{nl}
it seems.{waitkey}{clearbox}Ayase alone certainly{nl}
couldn't explain it{nl}
properly, could she?{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Brown totally bailed,{nl}
so Ayase and Elly had to{nl}
explain it to the teacher!{waitkey}{clearbox}Brown always makes himself{nl}
scarce at times like these!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Elly and Ayase didn't{nl}
faint, so they don't need{nl}
to go to the hospital.{waitkey}{clearbox}But why did only{nl}
we faint?{waitkey}{clearbox}The ones who didn't faint had{nl}
done the Persona ritual{nl}
before...{waitkey}{nl}
Ayase, Elly, and Brown...{waitkey}{ret}

Teacher: Hey, {ctl0f:1}.{nl}
Word is someone's been going{nl}
in and out of that empty room{nl}
at the end of the 2nd floor.{waitkey}{nl}
That's not you, is it?{waitkey}{ret}

Teacher: If it wasn't you,{nl}
then who's been sneaking{nl}
into that classroom...?{waitkey}{ret}
